extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements ManagedPropertyType

An implementation of the model object 'Managed Property Type'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Description
  • Display Name
  • Icon
  • Property Name
  • Property Class
  • Map Entries
  • Null Value
  • Value
  • List Entries
  • Id
